OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry day with some
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells. A few light
OL,7,Fshowers breaking out, these mainly
OL,8,Fover hills and coasts. Light to
OL,9,Fmoderate northwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA few showers will continue
OL,12,Facross the north through this evening
OL,13,Fand overnight. It will be dry
OL,14,Felsewhere with clear periods. Frost
OL,15,Fdeveloping under lengthy cloud breaks.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FA mainly dry and chilly start.
OL,18,FThickening cloud and rain will spread
OL,19,Fto the north by late morning and
OL,20,Felsewhere during the afternoon.
OL,21,FTurning drier through the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
