OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry, bright and cold on Monday,
OL,7,Fisolated showers at first. Early rain
OL,8,Fon Tuesday then bright with a few
OL,9,Fshowers. Rather cold with showers on
OL,10,FWednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
